meanings.definition: 硝子体下の、硝子膜下の
meanings.english_definition: Located beneath the hyaloid membrane of the vitreous body of the eye.

examples.sentence: Subhyalin hemorrhage can occur in the eye.
examples.translation: 硝子体下出血が眼に起こることがある。

etymology.value: From sub- (below) + hyalin (referring to the hyaloid membrane).
